Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.45,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正楷体_GBK\fs55\fsp0\fscy80\bord0.1\shad2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4D4C51&\4c&H000000&\fad(1008,0)\pos(952,716)}布魯諾·波美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,還有他們助理聚在一起
